column2: With our influence over the independent states in northern italy we can 'convince' them to join Sardinia-Piedmont if that suits our aims in the region.

In this year the house of Romanov shall celebrate the 300th anniversary of its succession to the russian throne as a young georgian named Joseph Vissarionovich Stalin travels to Vienna to further his studies.
即Small State Flag\n劬This flag dynamically assigns a size to this state. Currently it's set to Small since it's below 350k pops in 1836 OR 420k pops in 1870 OR 500k pops in 1900.
即Medium State Flag\n劬This flag dynamically assigns a size to this state. Currently it's set to Medium since it's below 680k pops in 1836 OR 760k pops in 1870 OR 820k pops in 1900.
即Large State Flag\n劬This flag dynamically assigns a size to this state. Currently it's set to Large since it's below 900k pops in 1836 OR 1m pops in 1870 OR 1,1m pops in 1900.
即Huge State Flag\n劬This flag dynamically assigns a size to this state. Currently it's set to Huge since it's above 900k pops in 1836 OR 1m pops in 1870 OR 1,1m pops in 1900.
